{"tid":128011,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登力量]今日唔見左個朋友想揾返","createTime":"2017-02-20T13:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T09:08:41.000Z","uid":48409,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58ffe156b7231ea299581a23f7bcf7d2c2f9cf7b","tid":128011,"uid":48409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:12:31.000Z","msg":"我個朋友係隻熊仔公仔<br />\n今日帶左佢出街影相就唔見咗<br />\n最後一次見佢嘅地方係海洋公園個灣景餐廳<br />\n5點左右去到油麻地地鐵站有響個袋到拎過嘢出嚟<br />\n之後又去過電影中心都有摷過個袋<br />\n再打開個袋就唔見咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我估計最大機會應該係響灣景餐廳/油麻地站/電影中心唔見咗佢<br />\n希望強大嘅連登仔可以幫我揾下佢<br />\n<br />\n(第一次開post 唔識貼圖)<br />\n佢個樣係咁嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ioc573f1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fioc573f1&h=e69fe638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日會再打電話問下op同去下油麻地站睇下有<br />\n冇人執到<br />\n我諗唔到仲有咩方法先揾佢<br />\n所以先響連登開post<br />\n<br />\n我同佢20年朋友<br />\n雖然唔係啲咩名牌公仔<br />\n但係我同佢有好多回憶<br />\n好想揾得返佢<br />\n希望有人見到嘅可以執返俾我<br />\n多謝大家！"},{"pid":"a8665d46748ef040bd2ee379b4b2f8d3249fe9b5","tid":128011,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:21:48.000Z","msg":"剩正評有用咩。。。推下啦"},{"pid":"3ce8efc6aac422519067affb00a75ab2d8ceeeea","tid":128011,"uid":76420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好得意"},{"pid":"7344eee9af7245f9e28468b02ca2aa2c8befd04f","tid":128011,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac687c118d1adc355476fdcf75653a261c603e04","tid":128011,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"例排都要響你老母架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我黎推post</span></span>"},{"pid":"63d8881a7bcbf8fb70109b